title: Bob Dylan - The Royal Albert Hall Concert - TQMP slavetothesound
description:
Amazing live recording of Bob Dylan at one of his most famous shows ever - The Royal Albert Hall in 1966.  This was released as "The Bootleg Series Vol. 4"  I really like the first disc full of his solo acoustic performance, but personally i prefer that over the second disc which he plays with a full band. Everyone knows Bob Dylan, I&#039;m not going to explain anymore  :)
